00:05:17.980 --> 00:05:21.700
and we understand that it's translated various ways,

00:05:21.700 --> 00:05:24.420
but the mischief that was intended to be done

00:05:24.420 --> 00:05:26.700
against Nehemiah and those that were doing the work,

